00:45:56.976 --> 00:46:00.466 A:middle
And when I did that, it gave
me an orange constraint.

WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:181083,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

00:45:56.976 --> 00:46:00.466 A:middle
And when I did that, it gave
